text: Boyan Dimitrov (, born 10 June 1916, date of death unknown) was a Bulgarian alpine skier. He competed in the men's combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1916 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Bulgarian male alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Bulgaria Category:Alpine skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
